edu.dynamic.dynamiz.UI

Class StyleUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.dynamic.dynamiz.UI.StyleUI

  • public class StyleUI
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the StyleUI class that will set the styling of the Styled Document. It recevies the styling settings from Displayer to UI to StyleUI before returning the style settings to UI
